description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP looks back at a surprising weekend in the NFL. Should there be concern surrounding the Bills? ESPN reporter Ed Werder discusses Dallas' upset loss to the Broncos. Was this a one off? And Carson Palmer makes his weekly appearance to recap Jordan Love's debut.
